Bosse_Halicarnassus_Status_Deep Freeze_D: Your body is encased in ice, preventing action and dealing damage over time.
Bosse_Halicarnassus_Status_Paralysis_Des: Deadened nerves are sometimes preventing the execution of actions.
Bosse_Halicarnassus_Status_Toad_Desc: Transformed into a toad and unable to execute actions.
Bosse_Unknown Source_Status_Haste_Desc: Weaponskill cast time and recast time, spell cast time and recast time, and auto-attack delay are reduced.
ContentDesc_Deltametrie 3.0: Fresh from your victory over the grotesque Catastrophe, you set your sights upon the next battle. Your foe is a being named Halicarnassus, an antagonist from a classical novel, wherein she rules as the Queen of Dimension Castle. Yet be it born of fact or fiction, the struggle ahead promises to be very real.
Instancecontenttextdata_17700_Text: There is no escape. You shall be a pawn in my games unto death.
Instancecontenttextdata_17708_Text: For a change of pace, let us play...an escape game!
Instancecontenttextdata_17709_Text: While you partake of the game, I shall partake of afternoon tea.
Instancecontenttextdata_17710_Text: A starry gift comes for you, but you'll not wish to be around to receive it.
Instancecontenttextdata_17711_Text: Escape swiftly, and you may well earn a prize.
Instancecontenttextdata_17712_Text: Well, well, returned before I could drain my cup. You deserve a prize.
Instancecontenttextdata_17713_Text: Hmph, I have long drained my cup. Such insolence to keep a lady waiting.
Instancecontenttextdata_17714_Text: Afternoon tea is over. Let us resume our fun-filled games.
Instancecontenttextdata_17715_Text: Dance is art in motion, and no one dances more artfully than I!
Instancecontenttextdata_17716_Text: My dance brings the board to life!
Instancecontenttextdata_17728_Text: Look upon these symbols. You will find them familiar.
Instancecontenttextdata_17729_Text: A shield to block, a sword to strike, a cross to heal. Choose wisely, or pay the price!
Instancecontenttextdata_17731_Text: Good, you understand the rules. You're clever. I like clever people.
Instancecontenttextdata_17738_Text: Now then, let us have a race. Run, run, as fast as you can!
